&lt;p&gt;After posted this solution as a comment on Kazi’s post I decided to polish this a little more and to actually provide a similar API as the MapRoute extension from the MVC framework. The idea is to provide a set of InsertRoute and InsertRouteAfter. &lt;/p&gt;
